cc:Work.dc:title: Misc - DiceTower
cc:Work.dc:description:
Tool for fairly rolling dice
Feel free to add a shallow ABox as a container for catching the dice so they don't scatter across the table.
You can also configure the DiceTower and change the number and angle of the ramps.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes DiceTower Command line short: boxes DiceTower
